fields.title: Need to build new app for Photos
fields.details:
I am a photographer and I take photos for my blog and news sites here in Iran. People are scared of my photos now, because they can be arrested for particpating in rallies.  I want to build an app that will keep their faces hidden—facebook recognizes faces, so we should be able to use the same technology to do this.
Who wants to help?!

fields.title: Attention & legal help for student activist!
fields.details:
My friend and fellow student Lui was arrested last week for teaching people how to circumvent online censorship, and we haven’t been able to speak to him since he was taken to the central prison outside of Beijing. 

Others students know that Lui is technologically savvy and asked him for getting around censors, so he set up a talk for a group them about circumvention tools and internet freedom.  He was arrested the next day.

I want to bring attention to his case and find out how we can help his defense. The media isn't covering it, and we don't know how he can defend himself.  Please help?!
